data.name: richTextBox2.Text
data.value:
1) Select a difficulty from the "Select Difficulty" dropdown in the upper right of the main window. 2) Click the "Randomize" button next to the difficulty setting to mix up the tiles based on your selected difficulty. 3) Solve the Puzzle. 4) Click the "Reset Puzzle" button near the bottom right corner of the main window to play again or restart in the middle of a game.
* At any time, you may restart the puzzle, or click the "Solve" button to display hints on how to solve the puzzle in the "Dialog Box".
